descript.purpose: Merged polygons of all teams from 2009 to 2011 season in Kazanluk, included. Useful for mathematical measurments, operation and calculations ( Counts are all proper) Dates and Leader columns have been deleted by Arc in the process of merging, therefore are unusable. Not good for general overview, but good for density displays and arithmetic operations.
